{
  "texts": [
    "The combination of covert communication and FL is expected to further enhance the security of ISAC systems [285].",
    "Specifically, FL allows ISAC nodes to upload their local models instead of the privacy data to the FL server, reducing the risk of data lock.",
    "Moreover, covert communication can protect the communication behavior from detection by various uncertainty techniques, such as transmit power uncertainty and noise uncertainty, which is an effective approach to guarantee the security of FL [286].",
    "Computing powerMany AI-enabled ISAC scenarios, such as V2X, not only deal with an enormous number of multi-modal data but also face the high real-time requirement, needing a high-performance computing hardware to deal with this issue.",
    "Moreover, some complicated AI models, such as large language models [287], also pose a higher requirement on computing power."
  ]
}